%h2 Hash Tags on Graph
%hr.star-primary
= image_tag "#{image_name}.png", class: "img-responsive img-centered"
%p 
  This application shows tweets stats on country map.
  
  If you wonder which state is more interested in your hastags, check it out.
%ul.list-inline.item-details
  %li 
    Date:
    %strong Oct 2014
  %li 
    %strong Opensource, Ruby, Rails
  %li
    %strong= link_to 'Github', 'https://github.com/anilmaurya/hash_tags_on_graph'
  %li
    %strong= link_to 'Site', 'http://coders.r14.railsrumble.com/'
= link_to '#', class: 'btn btn-default', data: {dismiss: 'modal'} do
  %i.fa.fa-times Close
